Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  ef  -  a  tale  of  memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.13,0:23:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有不想忘卻的回憶嗎


